WEBVTT

01:32.250 --> 01:34.950
[How dare you!?]

01:35.030 --> 01:38.030
[Episode 26]

01:53.509 --> 01:54.440
You sent her off?

01:56.710 --> 01:58.039
What are you looking at?

02:00.040 --> 02:01.240
Five stars aligning.

02:03.920 --> 02:06.380
I looked up
the Nameless's prophecy before.

02:07.230 --> 02:08.360
Five stars aligning

02:08.840 --> 02:10.750
refers to
this kind of celestial phenomenon.

02:10.750 --> 02:11.750
Ancient texts say

02:12.590 --> 02:15.390
this is an omen
of the monarch being assassinated.

02:18.400 --> 02:19.800
That's pretty accurate.

02:19.900 --> 02:20.960
It's not like that.

02:21.840 --> 02:22.770
Look carefully.

02:23.430 --> 02:25.360
Hasn't its tail already started to curve?

02:25.360 --> 02:26.910
It's not a straight line anymore.

02:26.910 --> 02:28.040
What does this mean?

02:28.520 --> 02:30.310
It means all of this has passed.

02:30.960 --> 02:32.690
Ever since you defeated Tu'er,

02:32.750 --> 02:34.870
you've already started
to change your fate.

02:34.870 --> 02:35.800
Since when

02:36.560 --> 02:38.280
do you believe in celestial signs so much?

02:38.280 --> 02:39.940
I believe in what benefits me.

02:42.430 --> 02:42.960
CEO Dan.

02:43.950 --> 02:45.680
Tomorrow,
at the Empress Dowager's funeral,

02:45.680 --> 02:47.140
I still want to be with you.

02:48.280 --> 02:50.079
We've already discussed this, Wanyin.

02:50.079 --> 02:52.310
But I just want peace of mind.

02:53.280 --> 02:54.480
You're taking risks,

02:54.870 --> 02:56.600
leaving me here waiting alone.

02:56.630 --> 02:57.890
Think about how I feel.

02:59.150 --> 03:00.480
You'll only feel at ease

03:00.560 --> 03:02.290
if we face the danger together?

03:03.310 --> 03:04.280
What about your position as Empress?

03:04.280 --> 03:05.740
You don't want it anymore?

03:06.680 --> 03:08.310
If we can't take down Prince Duan,

03:08.310 --> 03:10.240
this Empress title is just for show.

03:10.240 --> 03:13.040
I don't want to play cosplay
for the rest of my life.

03:13.960 --> 03:14.910
You mean...

03:16.590 --> 03:17.990
you'd rather die with me?

03:20.840 --> 03:23.050
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

03:23.340 --> 03:24.590
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

03:24.920 --> 03:27.060
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

03:25.870 --> 03:27.400
When I transmigrated here,

03:27.440 --> 03:28.760
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

03:28.430 --> 03:29.560
I already died once.

03:28.850 --> 03:31.340
♪ Words unspoken ♪

03:31.190 --> 03:32.240
I thought

03:32.780 --> 03:35.260
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

03:33.560 --> 03:35.160
I'd go to heaven after I died.

03:35.800 --> 03:37.590
I didn't expect to be thrown into
this hell-level script.

03:36.910 --> 03:39.090
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

03:39.370 --> 03:40.510
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

03:40.430 --> 03:41.400
There were many times

03:40.870 --> 03:42.870
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

03:42.750 --> 03:43.430
that I

03:43.370 --> 03:44.750
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

03:43.750 --> 03:45.310
felt exhausted and wanted to quit.

03:44.960 --> 03:47.290
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

03:47.870 --> 03:49.360
But because I have you on my team,

03:48.810 --> 03:52.150
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

03:50.910 --> 03:52.079
I somehow

03:52.770 --> 03:56.200
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

03:53.000 --> 03:54.120
made it this far.

03:56.910 --> 03:59.870
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

03:57.960 --> 03:59.560
We've done so much together—

04:00.400 --> 04:02.190
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

04:00.800 --> 04:02.060
preventing a drought,

04:02.440 --> 04:04.080
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

04:02.520 --> 04:04.000
defeating the Empress Dowager,

04:04.000 --> 04:04.910
and allying with Yan State.

04:04.380 --> 04:06.120
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

04:06.290 --> 04:08.530
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

04:06.360 --> 04:07.420
Even if it ends here

04:08.240 --> 04:08.920
and the game is over,

04:08.920 --> 04:12.040
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

04:10.240 --> 04:12.880
I still want to praise myself
for a job well done.

04:12.880 --> 04:15.220
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

04:13.320 --> 04:13.920
Of course,

04:14.570 --> 04:16.709
we still have many unfinished things

04:15.340 --> 04:16.510
♪ Still unchanged ♪

04:16.880 --> 04:19.779
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

04:17.120 --> 04:18.850
and many things to do together.

04:20.459 --> 04:21.820
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

04:20.630 --> 04:22.950
I'm also interested in the business empire
Xie Yong'er mentioned.

04:21.950 --> 04:26.530
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

04:24.830 --> 04:25.800
You promised me

04:26.510 --> 04:28.110
that no matter what happens,

04:28.560 --> 04:30.090
you'd never leave me alone.

04:31.240 --> 04:33.100
Do you want to break that promise?

04:37.360 --> 04:37.890
Alright.

04:39.560 --> 04:40.780
Then let's go together.

04:40.780 --> 04:44.340
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

04:44.860 --> 04:47.860
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

04:48.310 --> 04:50.240
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

04:50.430 --> 04:52.030
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

04:52.400 --> 04:54.040
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

04:54.390 --> 04:56.560
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

04:56.909 --> 05:00.110
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

05:00.870 --> 05:03.280
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

05:03.350 --> 05:04.470
♪ Still unchanged ♪

05:04.950 --> 05:07.840
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

05:08.410 --> 05:09.860
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

05:09.970 --> 05:17.320
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

05:36.360 --> 05:38.220
Her Majesty the Empress Dowager,

05:38.480 --> 05:39.870
a paragon of virtue.

05:41.190 --> 05:41.600
With

05:42.390 --> 05:43.750
her passing,

05:45.190 --> 05:46.650
the country and the people

05:47.120 --> 05:49.050
have lost a loving and kind mother.

05:49.560 --> 05:50.870
How mournful!

05:52.040 --> 05:53.600
The whole nation grieves!

05:54.920 --> 05:56.520
Her virtue endures forever,

05:57.720 --> 06:01.000
and she will be remembered
with honor for all ages!

06:02.930 --> 06:04.980
[Spirit Tablet of Empress Dowager
of Illustrious Virtue,]

06:04.980 --> 06:07.030
[Loyalty, Filial Piety, and Benevolence]

06:20.310 --> 06:21.000
Stop!

06:32.130 --> 06:32.930
Your Majesty,

06:33.820 --> 06:35.400
for this final stretch,

06:35.720 --> 06:38.380
you must walk beside the coffin
with the Empress

06:38.600 --> 06:40.550
to show your filial piety,

06:41.150 --> 06:42.270
so that everyone

06:42.630 --> 06:44.690
will know the kindness of your heart.

06:46.190 --> 06:47.320
The mounting stool!

07:11.890 --> 07:12.620
Your Majesty.

07:12.620 --> 07:14.640
[Spirit Tablet of Empress Dowager
of Illustrious Virtue,]

07:14.640 --> 07:16.660
[Loyalty, Filial Piety, and Benevolence]

08:04.220 --> 08:05.420
Protect the Emperor!

08:06.270 --> 08:06.930
Assassins!

08:07.390 --> 08:08.110
Yulin Guards!

08:08.110 --> 08:08.960
Protect His Majesty!

08:08.960 --> 08:10.750
You, come with me to catch the assassins!

08:10.750 --> 08:11.190
Yes!

08:37.549 --> 08:38.260
That way!

08:46.990 --> 08:47.650
Kneel!

08:48.960 --> 08:49.550
Kneel!

08:52.240 --> 08:53.030
Your Majesty,

08:53.030 --> 08:54.440
all assassins have been executed.

08:54.440 --> 08:55.010
However,

08:55.390 --> 08:57.270
I'm not sure
how to deal with their leader.

08:57.270 --> 08:59.600
Please make your decision, Your Majesty.

09:04.200 --> 09:05.360
How could it be him?

09:05.360 --> 09:07.180
Isn't this Zhao Wucheng,
wanted by the Imperial Guards?

09:07.180 --> 09:08.510
Wasn't he already dead?

09:08.870 --> 09:09.640
So...

09:09.870 --> 09:11.630
that body from before was fake?

09:16.530 --> 09:17.550
How could this happen?

09:17.550 --> 09:18.080
Exactly.

09:24.910 --> 09:25.970
You're quite bold,

09:26.440 --> 09:28.510
trying to assassinate me repeatedly.

09:28.510 --> 09:29.130
Tell me.

09:30.080 --> 09:31.410
Who are you working for?

09:38.510 --> 09:39.020
No one.

09:40.870 --> 09:42.330
I'm doing this for myself.

09:44.150 --> 09:46.010
But there is no grudge between us.

09:46.120 --> 09:47.200
Shameless tyrant.

09:48.440 --> 09:49.770
You're blinded by lust.

09:50.910 --> 09:53.240
Anyone would be justified in killing you!

09:55.550 --> 09:56.740
Well said.

09:57.030 --> 09:57.910
Quite bold.

09:58.720 --> 10:01.390
No wonder you were the former
commander of the Imperial Guards.

10:01.390 --> 10:03.120
Since you've escaped capture,

10:04.200 --> 10:06.050
why did you come back to die?

10:06.410 --> 10:07.840
You don't really think a single stone

10:07.840 --> 10:09.040
could kill me, do you?

10:09.150 --> 10:09.710
Speak!

10:10.320 --> 10:12.030
Who exactly is behind this?

10:20.120 --> 10:22.520
You just want me to say that name,
don't you?

10:23.080 --> 10:23.620
Fine.

10:23.870 --> 10:25.400
I'll give you what you want.

10:25.440 --> 10:28.080
The one who ordered me
to assassinate the Emperor is...

10:28.080 --> 10:29.780
Prince Duan, Xiahou Bo!

10:42.870 --> 10:43.670
Zhao Wucheng,

10:44.060 --> 10:45.390
you claim I ordered you.

10:47.000 --> 10:48.200
Do you have any proof?

10:48.270 --> 10:50.490
Everyone at court knows I work for you.

10:51.030 --> 10:52.290
Do I really need proof?

10:52.910 --> 10:54.080
If you work for me,

10:55.140 --> 10:57.150
why did you betray me so easily

10:57.840 --> 10:59.240
and confess it publicly?

11:05.570 --> 11:06.370
Your Majesty,

11:07.030 --> 11:09.840
I served on the frontier
and earned military merits.

11:09.840 --> 11:12.500
Rumors then spread
that the army was loyal to me.

11:12.870 --> 11:14.960
After I returned to the capital to report
and handed over command,

11:14.960 --> 11:17.220
the Imperial Guards became mine as well.

11:17.270 --> 11:18.310
This Zhao Wucheng

11:18.550 --> 11:20.600
attempted rebellion on Mount Bei twice.

11:20.600 --> 11:22.320
Without any proof,

11:22.670 --> 11:24.670
he claimed he acted under my orders.

11:24.790 --> 11:26.240
So I have to ask,

11:27.550 --> 11:28.790
who ordered him

11:29.550 --> 11:30.850
to frame me?

11:35.390 --> 11:36.630
Th-This assassin...

11:36.650 --> 11:38.110
I know him, Your Highness!

11:38.150 --> 11:38.990
Isn't this...

11:39.630 --> 11:41.890
a servant from Minister Yu's residence?

11:47.720 --> 11:49.030
This one too!

11:49.440 --> 11:50.750
A few days ago,

11:50.750 --> 11:52.000
when I visited the Yu Residence,

11:52.000 --> 11:53.660
he was the one who received me.

11:55.790 --> 11:57.000
Minister Yu,

11:58.670 --> 12:00.260
why are you framing me?

12:03.870 --> 12:04.670
Your Majesty!

12:05.270 --> 12:05.750
I...

12:06.670 --> 12:08.770
know nothing about this!

12:09.270 --> 12:10.000
Th-There...

12:10.240 --> 12:10.980
must be...

12:11.360 --> 12:13.360
some misunderstandings!

12:13.630 --> 12:14.750
Your Majesty!

12:15.150 --> 12:15.880
Minister Yu!

12:16.230 --> 12:18.130
You usually seem so honest,

12:18.360 --> 12:20.240
yet you're connected to assassins

12:20.240 --> 12:21.790
and trying to pin this on Prince Duan!

12:21.790 --> 12:23.030
What are your intentions?

12:23.030 --> 12:23.600
Lord Cao!

12:23.960 --> 12:25.120
Don't talk nonsense!

12:25.120 --> 12:25.780
Minister Yu

12:26.080 --> 12:27.790
has never been involved
in factional disputes.

12:27.790 --> 12:29.600
How could he suddenly be connected
to assassins?

12:29.600 --> 12:30.130
Exactly!

12:31.120 --> 12:33.440
Besides, Minister Yu
just became the Imperial Father-in-law.

12:33.440 --> 12:35.040
Giving up his family's glory

12:35.080 --> 12:37.880
and conspiring with a traitor
to kill the Emperor?

12:37.910 --> 12:38.670
Has he lost his mind?

12:38.670 --> 12:40.720
You can know a person's face,
but not their heart.

12:40.720 --> 12:42.150
To know the truth,

12:42.150 --> 12:43.910
we should ask Zhao Wucheng.

12:45.000 --> 12:45.800
Zhao Wucheng,

12:46.790 --> 12:48.030
what's your explanation?

12:48.030 --> 12:48.870
I told you,

12:50.120 --> 12:51.390
I did it for myself.

12:51.790 --> 12:53.050
You didn't believe me,

12:53.120 --> 12:55.180
and forced me to accuse someone else.

12:56.390 --> 12:57.750
I accused Prince Duan,

12:58.840 --> 13:00.840
yet you didn't believe that either.

13:01.200 --> 13:02.480
You, as an emperor,

13:03.080 --> 13:04.510
are truly hard to please.

13:05.440 --> 13:06.700
No wonder the one I love

13:07.970 --> 13:10.840
is trying everything to kill you.

13:10.870 --> 13:11.740
Outrageous!

13:12.200 --> 13:14.600
How dare you speak to His Majesty
like that?

13:14.670 --> 13:15.470
Commander Fu.

13:16.000 --> 13:16.480
Yes.

13:16.910 --> 13:17.720
Search him.

13:17.910 --> 13:18.270
Yes.

13:20.630 --> 13:21.180
Stop!

13:21.300 --> 13:21.960
Don't move!

13:30.450 --> 13:30.900
[Ever since we met
at the New Year flower market,]

13:30.900 --> 13:31.360
[I haven't been able to forget you]

13:31.390 --> 13:32.280
[I know your feelings for me.
Yet I'm entering]

13:32.300 --> 13:33.300
[the palace tomorrow,
and we'll hardly meet again]

13:35.910 --> 13:36.710
Your Majesty,

13:37.030 --> 13:38.560
These are some love letters

13:38.560 --> 13:39.610
between him...

13:39.840 --> 13:40.620
and a woman.

13:43.510 --> 13:44.610
And this is a...

13:45.270 --> 13:47.230
uniquely embroidered sachet.

14:00.960 --> 14:01.660
Are these

14:01.740 --> 14:03.340
truly written by Consort Yu?

14:03.630 --> 14:04.170
Yes.

14:06.480 --> 14:07.510
Even this sachet

14:08.690 --> 14:10.890
was embroidered by her own hands for me.

14:11.300 --> 14:12.700
The fabric of this sachet

14:12.870 --> 14:14.760
is silk tribute from Qiang State.

14:15.630 --> 14:16.290
But this...

14:16.600 --> 14:19.260
This was only given to the consorts
in the harem.

14:19.960 --> 14:22.360
And this letter paper
also looks like it's from the palace.

14:22.360 --> 14:23.370
Could it be...

14:23.840 --> 14:25.070
that Zhao Wucheng

14:25.200 --> 14:26.600
is involved

14:27.000 --> 14:28.260
with a palace consort?

14:28.480 --> 14:29.880
Shameless Zhao Wucheng!

14:30.480 --> 14:31.610
We can easily verify

14:32.080 --> 14:33.740
who this evidence belongs to.

14:34.240 --> 14:35.180
At this point,

14:36.510 --> 14:38.310
you'd better confess the truth.

14:42.840 --> 14:43.510
Fine.

14:46.050 --> 14:46.850
I'll tell you.

14:49.200 --> 14:50.860
This person is none other than

14:51.720 --> 14:53.520
the most favored Yu...

15:01.000 --> 15:02.270
Shameless villain.

15:03.620 --> 15:05.550
You don't deserve to taint my ears.

15:12.390 --> 15:14.630
Your Majesty,
why were you so eager to kill him?

15:14.630 --> 15:16.560
Are you not going to investigate

15:17.150 --> 15:19.000
whether this sachet
was embroidered by Consort Yu,

15:19.000 --> 15:21.000
or whether they committed adultery

15:21.390 --> 15:22.670
and engaged in illicit acts?

15:22.670 --> 15:23.400
Impossible!

15:23.550 --> 15:25.670
How could Empress Yu
be the person you describe?

15:25.670 --> 15:26.840
How is it impossible?

15:26.840 --> 15:29.770
These assassins
are servants from the Yu Residence!

15:29.870 --> 15:32.330
Your Majesty,
are you really going to strike

15:32.390 --> 15:34.590
your own brother for the sake of a woman?

15:38.720 --> 15:39.510
Xiahou Bo,

15:41.000 --> 15:42.600
are you staging a rebellion?

15:43.150 --> 15:45.880
Your Majesty,
you can ignore our brotherly ties,

15:46.320 --> 15:49.180
but I must ask one question
for the sake of the realm.

15:49.600 --> 15:52.200
The Empress Dowager
was always in good health.

15:52.630 --> 15:54.290
Why did she suddenly pass away

15:54.750 --> 15:56.340
after going to Mount Bei?

15:57.790 --> 15:58.880
And Zhao Wucheng—

15:59.600 --> 16:01.310
how did he escape unscathed

16:01.480 --> 16:03.340
while under a city-wide manhunt?

16:04.310 --> 16:06.770
Did he really have an affair
with Empress Yu?

16:07.670 --> 16:09.390
Deposing the Crown Prince,
crowning the Empress,

16:09.390 --> 16:11.840
killing loyal ministers,
favoring relatives by marriage—

16:11.840 --> 16:12.640
Your Majesty,

16:13.750 --> 16:16.280
have you been deceived
by the demonic empress

16:17.030 --> 16:19.050
and lost your judgment?

16:19.320 --> 16:20.000
Your Highness Prince Duan!

16:20.000 --> 16:20.840
Shut up!

16:21.120 --> 16:22.480
Can't you see the situation?

16:22.480 --> 16:23.790
The verbal battle is over.

16:23.790 --> 16:24.710
Soldiers!

16:24.910 --> 16:25.640
Here!

16:26.240 --> 16:27.970
Eliminate the demonic empress

16:28.150 --> 16:29.600
to purge His Majesty's side!

16:29.600 --> 16:30.610
Yulin Guards!

16:30.840 --> 16:31.390
Here!

16:31.600 --> 16:32.800
Protect the Empress!

16:33.440 --> 16:35.140
Uphold the truth!

16:35.360 --> 16:36.080
Yes!

16:36.870 --> 16:38.000
Kill!

16:38.120 --> 16:41.200
Kill!

16:49.680 --> 16:50.960
That scoundrel Xiahou Bo

16:50.960 --> 16:52.360
has actually colluded
with the Central Army.

16:52.360 --> 16:53.620
Why was there no alarm?

16:53.670 --> 16:54.670
It must have been when General Luo
of the Central Army

16:54.670 --> 16:55.720
returned to court to report

16:55.720 --> 16:57.150
that he left some men behind.

16:57.150 --> 16:58.840
Since then, they've been hiding nearby,

16:58.840 --> 17:00.750
waiting for Prince Duan
to give the signal.

17:00.750 --> 17:01.320
Let's go!

17:19.200 --> 17:20.160
Li, you...

17:20.349 --> 17:20.880
Are you alright?

17:20.880 --> 17:21.410
I'm fine.

17:21.720 --> 17:22.290
Good.

17:22.510 --> 17:23.369
Where's Er Lan?

17:24.050 --> 17:24.510
I...

17:28.319 --> 17:28.720
You...

17:29.310 --> 17:29.710
You...

17:30.370 --> 17:31.670
Li, where are you...

17:32.150 --> 17:33.500
Where are you going?

17:36.570 --> 17:37.230
Er Lan!

17:38.110 --> 17:38.720
Er Lan!

17:39.590 --> 17:40.440
Why are you going up there?

17:40.440 --> 17:41.570
We're outnumbered.

17:41.640 --> 17:43.550
We must push the giant stone
down the mountain.

17:43.550 --> 17:43.950
Er Lan!

17:44.550 --> 17:45.090
Er Lan!

17:50.400 --> 17:51.880
Prince Duan's men already went up there.

17:51.880 --> 17:53.110
You'll only die if you go up.

17:53.110 --> 17:54.640
His Majesty and Her Majesty
cannot be left unprotected.

17:54.640 --> 17:55.880
Don't worry about me. Go back.

17:55.880 --> 17:56.370
Er Lan!

17:56.610 --> 17:57.180
Er Lan!

17:58.550 --> 17:59.110
I'll go.

17:59.640 --> 18:00.350
I'll go, alright?

18:00.350 --> 18:01.620
What are you talking about?

18:01.620 --> 18:04.280
Li, don't you always
want to be a pillar in court?

18:04.350 --> 18:05.700
You must live to that day.

18:05.700 --> 18:06.500
You're right.

18:06.880 --> 18:09.030
I joined the court
to make a name for myself.

18:09.030 --> 18:10.640
So don't try to steal that opportunity.

18:10.640 --> 18:12.130
At least I'm strong enough

18:12.510 --> 18:13.570
to move that stone.

18:14.400 --> 18:14.920
Li!

18:18.200 --> 18:19.180
I am a woman.

18:20.960 --> 18:23.040
My presence in court is already improper.

18:23.040 --> 18:24.840
Leaving is only a matter of time.

18:25.420 --> 18:26.360
Go back, Li.

18:27.680 --> 18:28.810
Great Xia needs you.

18:35.640 --> 18:36.230
Li?

18:36.440 --> 18:37.370
How inappropriate.

18:37.370 --> 18:37.930
Hey!

18:38.270 --> 18:40.200
Why are you standing here in a daze?

18:41.200 --> 18:42.040
Er Lan is up there.

18:42.040 --> 18:43.500
Let's go save her quickly!

19:00.920 --> 19:01.980
Catch that demon!

19:02.230 --> 19:02.800
Wanyin!

19:05.750 --> 19:06.590
Your Highness,

19:06.590 --> 19:07.670
should we strike while the iron is hot

19:07.670 --> 19:08.520
and just...

19:08.550 --> 19:08.830
No.

19:09.680 --> 19:10.940
We'll hold her hostage

19:11.200 --> 19:13.000
to force the Emperor to withdraw

19:13.510 --> 19:15.600
and return to the palace to be confined.

19:15.600 --> 19:17.260
The Emperor cannot die today.

19:17.830 --> 19:19.030
Especially not here.

19:20.000 --> 19:23.180
He must be bewitched
by the demonic empress Yu Wanyin,

19:23.830 --> 19:25.830
and then go mad and die in the palace.

19:27.550 --> 19:28.240
Who are you?

19:28.830 --> 19:29.590
Go check

19:29.720 --> 19:31.320
where Prince Duan's men are.

19:34.400 --> 19:34.950
Indeed.

19:35.190 --> 19:36.590
Down there are all Prince Duan's men.

19:36.590 --> 19:38.550
Push the giant stone down the mountain!

19:38.550 --> 19:39.080
Alright!

19:42.590 --> 19:43.240
One!

19:43.510 --> 19:44.100
Two!

19:44.440 --> 19:45.070
Three!

19:47.750 --> 19:48.240
An Xian.

19:49.830 --> 19:51.290
If anything happens to me,

19:51.420 --> 19:52.610
protect yourself

19:53.880 --> 19:55.280
and keep the palace secure.

19:55.280 --> 19:56.080
Your Majesty,

19:56.170 --> 19:57.330
what are you saying?

19:57.640 --> 19:59.700
I exercised with Her Majesty as well.

20:16.080 --> 20:16.840
You demon.

20:17.400 --> 20:18.980
I gave you a chance,

20:20.420 --> 20:21.790
but you didn't take it.

20:32.110 --> 20:32.830
Who are you?

20:33.750 --> 20:35.080
Mind your own business.

21:00.110 --> 21:01.310
Push harder!

21:34.840 --> 21:36.210
Dan, come with me!

21:36.550 --> 21:37.510
Mr. Bei, I can't leave yet.

21:37.510 --> 21:38.880
-I haven't make Great Xia...
-No!

21:38.880 --> 21:39.680
We must go now!

21:39.950 --> 21:40.350
Hurry!

21:40.640 --> 21:42.000
We're giving up the throne!

21:42.000 --> 21:43.330
Your Majesty, let's go!

21:47.210 --> 21:47.880
Your Highness!

21:47.880 --> 21:49.160
-Your Highness!
-Your Highness!

21:49.160 --> 21:50.230
Hurry!

21:50.310 --> 21:51.750
Lift it up!

21:56.350 --> 21:57.080
Lift it up!

21:59.950 --> 22:00.830
Lift it up!

22:01.830 --> 22:02.500
My leg...

22:03.550 --> 22:04.850
My leg!

22:05.270 --> 22:06.130
Your Highness!

22:06.480 --> 22:07.040
Your Highness!

22:07.040 --> 22:08.240
Your Highness, how do you feel?

22:08.240 --> 22:09.160
Go back to the city,

22:09.160 --> 22:10.310
and get the imperial physician!

22:10.310 --> 22:11.820
Where is Xiahou Dan?

22:12.030 --> 22:12.510
Your Highness!

22:12.510 --> 22:12.830
Your Highness!

22:12.830 --> 22:14.030
That expert carried him away and escaped.

22:14.030 --> 22:14.690
After them!

22:15.030 --> 22:15.500
Yes!

22:15.640 --> 22:16.310
Yes, Your Highness!

22:16.310 --> 22:17.440
I want him alive!

22:17.440 --> 22:17.960
Yes!

22:21.440 --> 22:22.280
From the looks of it,

22:22.280 --> 22:23.640
the outcome is already decided.

22:23.640 --> 22:24.720
Where is His Majesty?

22:24.720 --> 22:25.720
Why isn't he here?

22:26.880 --> 22:27.280
Hurry!

22:27.400 --> 22:28.750
-Hurry!
-Let's go!

22:31.640 --> 22:32.040
Hurry!

22:32.800 --> 22:34.590
Prince Duan planned such a grand scheme

22:34.590 --> 22:36.030
just to usurp the throne.

22:36.480 --> 22:39.000
Now that Prince Duan is returning
to the capital unharmed,

22:39.000 --> 22:41.310
could it be that something happened
to His Majesty?

22:41.310 --> 22:42.180
If His Majesty had died,

22:42.180 --> 22:44.270
Prince Duan
wouldn't have left in such haste.

22:44.270 --> 22:45.310
And if Prince Duan had won,

22:45.310 --> 22:46.710
it wouldn't have ended so abruptly,

22:46.710 --> 22:48.110
leaving this mess behind.

22:48.110 --> 22:48.550
Look.

22:49.880 --> 22:53.010
Even the Empress Dowager's coffin
was left unattended.

23:04.550 --> 23:05.350
You're awake?

23:06.350 --> 23:06.790
Get up.

23:16.680 --> 23:17.720
Why am I here?

23:18.480 --> 23:19.260
You tell me.

23:22.000 --> 23:22.920
Xiahou Dan!

23:23.990 --> 23:25.050
Stop the carriage.

23:28.790 --> 23:30.040
Stop right now.

23:30.480 --> 23:31.510
I was ordered

23:31.590 --> 23:33.350
to escort you out of the capital
at the risk of my life.

23:33.350 --> 23:34.680
No matter what happens,

23:34.680 --> 23:36.080
I cannot leave your side.

23:36.240 --> 23:38.400
I'm telling you
to stop the carriage immediately!

23:38.400 --> 23:39.800
Don't waste your energy.

23:40.400 --> 23:41.800
They won't listen to you.

23:43.030 --> 23:43.830
I must say,

23:44.310 --> 23:45.930
Xiao Tiancai is quite something.

23:45.930 --> 23:48.720
That sleeping drug
kept you unconscious for 2 full hours.

23:48.720 --> 23:49.750
You knew about this?

23:49.750 --> 23:50.890
I didn't.

23:51.000 --> 23:52.200
I absolutely didn't.

23:52.510 --> 23:54.370
I was going to leave this morning,

23:54.480 --> 23:56.680
but Xiahou Dan secretly put you in here.

23:56.830 --> 23:58.310
He kept it from you

23:58.390 --> 23:59.650
until the last moment,

23:59.720 --> 24:02.650
probably to prevent anyone
from leaking the secret.

24:03.480 --> 24:04.400
Alright.

24:04.550 --> 24:06.170
Stop being so angry.

24:06.190 --> 24:07.730
He did it for your own good.

24:09.560 --> 24:11.400
How's everything going at Mount Bei?

24:11.400 --> 24:12.130
I don't know.

24:13.070 --> 24:14.020
I plan to

24:14.240 --> 24:15.920
find a place to settle down first,

24:15.920 --> 24:17.030
then send someone to gather information.

24:17.030 --> 24:17.760
Is that okay?

24:20.480 --> 24:22.680
Just enjoy the view outside the window.

24:25.960 --> 24:27.190
I'm finally free.

24:30.800 --> 24:32.060
Protect Her Highness!

24:32.130 --> 24:33.060
It's a tripwire!

24:41.550 --> 24:42.480
Are you alright?

24:42.720 --> 24:43.270
I'm fine.

24:43.510 --> 24:44.750
-Are you hurt anywhere?
-What about you?

24:44.750 --> 24:45.280
I'm fine.

24:45.680 --> 24:46.640
Your Majesty,

24:48.070 --> 24:50.810
would you kindly crawl out yourself?

24:52.400 --> 24:53.290
Prince Duan

24:53.960 --> 24:54.720
ordered me

24:55.200 --> 24:57.240
to escort Empress Yu
to return to the palace.

24:57.240 --> 24:57.920
It's Mu Yun.

24:58.720 --> 25:00.180
It's best if you're alive,

25:00.200 --> 25:01.800
but it's fine if you're dead.

25:03.960 --> 25:04.960
Empress Yu,

25:05.800 --> 25:06.750
you'd better

25:06.750 --> 25:08.950
-climb out obediently.
-There's a gun.

25:09.740 --> 25:12.550
Don't make me set the carriage on fire.

25:14.790 --> 25:17.840
If your face gets burned
beyond recognition,

25:18.300 --> 25:19.350
-It'll be hard for me...
-Don't panic.

25:19.350 --> 25:20.350
Pull it out first.

25:20.660 --> 25:22.120
To explain to Prince Duan.

25:23.070 --> 25:23.440
Yong'er!

25:23.440 --> 25:24.300
I'll stall him!

25:29.880 --> 25:30.590
Mr. Mu,

25:31.440 --> 25:33.040
you've got the wrong person.

25:33.240 --> 25:33.920
It's me.

25:35.310 --> 25:35.880
Mr. Mu,

25:36.130 --> 25:36.950
why did you...

25:37.790 --> 25:39.390
You've got the wrong person.

25:39.480 --> 25:41.400
Isn't this Consort Xie?

25:43.160 --> 25:43.720
Mr. Mu,

25:44.400 --> 25:46.170
you said Prince Duan sent you here.

25:46.170 --> 25:47.230
I don't believe it.

25:48.110 --> 25:49.960
You were dismissed from your position
long ago.

25:49.960 --> 25:51.270
You didn't even have the right

25:51.270 --> 25:53.110
to attend the Empress Dowager's funeral.

25:53.110 --> 25:53.890
I guess

25:54.480 --> 25:57.270
you're just looking for a chance
to redeem yourself

25:57.270 --> 25:58.870
and get back in favor, right?

25:59.350 --> 26:01.400
But after serving Prince Duan for so long,

26:01.400 --> 26:03.860
you must know
what kind of person he truly is.

26:04.640 --> 26:06.160
He appears benevolent,

26:06.680 --> 26:08.250
but is actually narrow-minded.

26:08.250 --> 26:09.060
Look at me.

26:09.790 --> 26:11.400
I'm a living example.

26:12.400 --> 26:12.830
Mr. Mu,

26:13.720 --> 26:14.680
take my advice.

26:16.030 --> 26:17.630
Prince Duan is no good ruler.

26:18.240 --> 26:19.720
His Majesty is kind-hearted.

26:19.720 --> 26:21.640
If you join me
in turning against Prince Duan,

26:21.640 --> 26:23.370
he will surely spare your life.

26:24.750 --> 26:25.480
His Majesty?

26:30.790 --> 26:31.200
He...

26:31.350 --> 26:34.000
He can barely save himself now.

26:34.870 --> 26:35.710
At this point,

26:36.160 --> 26:39.450
he might already be a corpse.

26:41.880 --> 26:43.180
You guessed right.

26:43.720 --> 26:45.150
My waiting here

26:45.170 --> 26:47.030
is indeed my last desperate move.

26:47.160 --> 26:48.600
I was taking a gamble

26:49.590 --> 26:52.050
that His Majesty
would send Empress Yu away.

26:52.680 --> 26:53.830
I was also betting

26:54.400 --> 26:56.760
that they'd choose a secluded path.

26:57.550 --> 26:59.880
I pride myself on reading people.

27:00.440 --> 27:03.310
I should have been the one
skillfully balancing all sides,

27:03.310 --> 27:05.000
all the factions

27:05.160 --> 27:07.220
desperately trying to win me over.

27:08.110 --> 27:09.000
But now,

27:09.270 --> 27:11.330
I have to be

27:11.440 --> 27:13.650
a strategist without a position.

27:14.590 --> 27:15.400
Tell me,

27:16.030 --> 27:16.880
who is to blame

27:17.550 --> 27:18.920
for all of this?

27:18.940 --> 27:19.490
Mr. Mu,

27:20.270 --> 27:21.770
you should know very well

27:22.310 --> 27:25.110
that there's no such thing
as balancing all sides.

27:25.200 --> 27:26.070
If there were,

27:29.440 --> 27:31.270
you'd only end up
being scorned by all sides.

27:31.270 --> 27:33.290
What a sharp tongue.

27:33.550 --> 27:35.550
If it weren't for a traitor like you,

27:36.590 --> 27:38.030
how would I, Murong Yunji,

27:38.030 --> 27:39.490
have come to this?

27:39.720 --> 27:42.080
With your petty tricks,

27:42.480 --> 27:44.110
you actually think you can save

27:44.110 --> 27:45.710
the person in that carriage?

27:46.720 --> 27:48.240
I'm not like His Highness.

27:48.440 --> 27:50.550
I won't be seduced by your beauty.

27:51.000 --> 27:51.830
Rest assured.

27:53.680 --> 27:55.360
None of you...

27:56.350 --> 27:57.440
will escape.

28:20.000 --> 28:20.790
Did I scare you?

28:20.790 --> 28:21.320
Yong'er!

28:22.750 --> 28:23.280
Yong'er!

28:28.750 --> 28:29.350
Help!

28:30.070 --> 28:31.000
Physician Xiao!

28:31.070 --> 28:32.330
Where is Xiao Tiancai?

28:33.110 --> 28:33.970
Did you forget?

28:34.640 --> 28:35.430
He said...

28:36.200 --> 28:37.860
he would stay in the palace...

28:38.240 --> 28:39.770
in exchange for my freedom.

28:40.110 --> 28:40.960
Let's go back.

28:41.310 --> 28:42.640
Let's go back right now.

28:42.750 --> 28:43.000
Let's go!

28:43.000 --> 28:43.440
No!

28:44.200 --> 28:44.930
Listen to me,

28:45.400 --> 28:46.030
Sis.

28:47.000 --> 28:47.720
If

28:48.000 --> 28:49.110
Xiao Tiancai

28:49.400 --> 28:50.830
finds out I'm dying,

28:52.720 --> 28:53.780
he'll go on strike.

28:54.920 --> 28:56.210
At a time like this,

28:56.750 --> 28:57.950
you're still joking?

28:59.200 --> 29:00.270
I won't let you die.

29:01.530 --> 29:04.120
I said I would invest
in your business empire.

29:04.510 --> 29:06.110
We'll run food and package
delivery businesses

29:06.110 --> 29:06.750
together,

29:07.880 --> 29:09.190
making them big.

29:09.350 --> 29:09.880
Alright?

29:12.030 --> 29:12.880
Don't cry.

29:13.130 --> 29:15.820
♪ In the time and space of chaos ♪

29:13.920 --> 29:14.640
Don't cry.

29:16.310 --> 29:16.930
Maybe...

29:16.650 --> 29:19.720
♪ Every time I open my eyes ♪

29:17.920 --> 29:20.260
it's all just been a dream.

29:20.340 --> 29:23.660
♪ Your silhouette is engraved inside ♪

29:20.590 --> 29:21.400
When I wake up,

29:22.830 --> 29:25.220
I can go back to the outside world.

29:25.920 --> 29:28.180
I'll never argue with my mom again.

29:26.720 --> 29:29.470
♪ Then we transform ♪

29:29.550 --> 29:30.510
I also want...

29:30.100 --> 29:33.160
♪ Into the blazing light to guard ♪

29:31.510 --> 29:34.040
to go with you
to that city you mentioned...

29:33.540 --> 29:38.210
♪ Our eternal galaxy ♪

29:35.110 --> 29:36.960
and try that fermented bean drink.

29:36.960 --> 29:37.750
I'm sorry.

29:39.040 --> 29:41.490
♪ Watch the universe bow ♪

29:39.360 --> 29:40.680
I'm really sorry.

29:42.210 --> 29:44.870
♪ And let time freeze ♪

29:43.830 --> 29:44.640
Wanyin,

29:45.520 --> 29:51.300
♪ I still gaze into those firm eyes ♪

29:47.200 --> 29:49.000
I'm also a 2D character,

29:50.000 --> 29:50.590
right?

29:51.400 --> 29:52.070
No.

29:51.650 --> 29:53.010
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

29:52.480 --> 29:53.440
You're not!

29:53.620 --> 29:56.540
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

29:55.200 --> 29:56.350
I really love...

29:57.000 --> 29:58.680
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

29:57.120 --> 29:59.280
our gossip sessions in the dorm.

29:58.700 --> 30:04.650
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

30:00.480 --> 30:01.350
If only...

30:05.000 --> 30:05.720
If only...

30:05.140 --> 30:06.600
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

30:07.070 --> 30:09.980
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

30:08.030 --> 30:09.110
we could become...

30:09.480 --> 30:11.320
sisters a little earlier.

30:10.560 --> 30:12.700
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

30:12.800 --> 30:14.330
♪ We can dance together ♪

30:12.920 --> 30:13.670
Wanyin...

30:14.350 --> 30:23.950
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

30:16.550 --> 30:17.680
I'm free now.

30:35.160 --> 30:35.750
Yong'er!

30:38.000 --> 30:38.960
Xie Yong'er!

30:42.350 --> 30:43.550
Yong'er!

30:46.650 --> 30:49.190
♪ Watch the universe bow ♪

30:50.110 --> 30:52.530
♪ And let time freeze ♪

30:53.240 --> 30:59.010
♪ I still gaze into those firm eyes ♪

30:59.430 --> 31:00.510
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

31:01.210 --> 31:04.000
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

31:04.640 --> 31:06.210
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

31:06.230 --> 31:12.230
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

31:12.830 --> 31:14.110
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

31:14.790 --> 31:17.660
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

31:18.140 --> 31:20.250
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

31:19.400 --> 31:20.310
It's a deal then!

31:20.270 --> 31:21.910
♪ We can dance together ♪

31:21.350 --> 31:23.250
When I get
my food delivery business going,

31:21.940 --> 31:29.650
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

31:23.680 --> 31:24.720
you have to teach me

31:24.720 --> 31:26.380
more of your hometown snacks.

31:30.790 --> 31:32.550
With mountains and rivers as witness,

31:32.550 --> 31:34.150
and the sun and moon as proof.

31:34.920 --> 31:35.450
Yong'er,

31:38.270 --> 31:39.790
may your soul return home

31:39.930 --> 31:41.110
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

31:41.490 --> 31:42.620
and enjoy peace.

31:41.770 --> 31:44.560
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

31:45.200 --> 31:46.770
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

31:46.830 --> 31:52.740
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

31:53.450 --> 31:55.030
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

31:55.330 --> 31:58.260
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

31:58.700 --> 32:00.810
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

32:00.830 --> 32:02.470
♪ We can dance together ♪

32:02.500 --> 32:10.260
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

32:13.280 --> 32:19.300
♪ Never looking back ♪

32:25.160 --> 32:25.640
Mr. Bei.

32:26.590 --> 32:27.380
Put me down

32:28.240 --> 32:29.440
and escape yourself.

32:30.590 --> 32:31.790
Even if the sky falls,

32:32.000 --> 32:33.400
I won't leave you behind.

32:36.240 --> 32:38.400
My life
is already coming to an end anyway.

32:38.400 --> 32:39.060
Nonsense.

32:39.920 --> 32:42.120
As long as you're not this damn emperor,

32:42.720 --> 32:44.450
you'll surely live a long life.

32:45.270 --> 32:45.680
I...

32:46.350 --> 32:47.880
will find medicine for you.

32:48.550 --> 32:49.960
I'm not her child.

32:56.110 --> 32:57.200
I'm not Xiahou Dan.

32:59.440 --> 33:01.830
I'm just a lone soul living in this body.

33:02.880 --> 33:03.940
Everything before

33:05.350 --> 33:06.270
was all my lies.

33:09.080 --> 33:09.590
Mr. Bei,

33:10.240 --> 33:11.680
do you understand? I'm not...

33:11.680 --> 33:12.700
I understand.

33:19.640 --> 33:20.900
You're not her child.

33:24.270 --> 33:24.870
I'm sorry.

33:27.160 --> 33:27.960
Your Majesty!

33:29.920 --> 33:30.720
Your Majesty,

33:30.920 --> 33:31.820
they're catching up!

33:31.820 --> 33:32.820
We must leave now!

33:34.510 --> 33:36.040
If Nan'er were still alive,

33:38.140 --> 33:39.830
she wouldn't want to see Dan—

33:40.350 --> 33:41.080
you—suffer.

33:43.440 --> 33:44.160
But I

33:45.480 --> 33:46.940
can only take you this far.

33:47.510 --> 33:48.310
Your Majesty!

33:48.590 --> 33:50.790
If we don't leave now, it'll be too late!

33:53.640 --> 33:54.750
Take His Majesty away!

33:54.750 --> 33:55.160
Yes!

33:55.680 --> 33:57.280
Let's take His Majesty away!

33:57.920 --> 33:58.470
Your Majesty!
